325
00:14:46,870 --> 00:14:47,930
When the captain died,

326
00:14:47,930 --> 00:14:48,440
I saw

327
00:14:48,470 --> 00:14:49,730
Young Lord Yin nearby.

328
00:14:50,150 --> 00:14:51,140
